# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Rust / Cargo
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
target/
Cargo.lock          # uncomment to track lockfile for applications

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Solana / SBF
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Compiled program binaries
*.so
# Exception: the Jupiter V6 program binary lives under contracts/axis-g3m/fixtures
# and is committed so CI workflows can launch a forked validator without
# round-tripping through mainnet RPC (mainnet-beta + the public mirrors
# proved too flaky for a hard CI dependency). Refresh via
# scripts/ops/refresh-jupiter-fixture.sh on Jupiter V6 upgrades.
!contracts/axis-g3m/fixtures/jupiter_v6.so
# Exception: minimal mock Jupiter program used by axis-vault WithdrawSol
# bound tests. Source under contracts/ab-integration-tests/mock-jupiter,
# rebuild via `cargo build-sbf --manifest-path
# contracts/ab-integration-tests/mock-jupiter/Cargo.toml` and re-copy.
!contracts/ab-integration-tests/fixtures/mock_jupiter.so
deploy/

# Test validator ledger data (can be gigabytes)
test-ledger/
ledger/

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Node.js / TypeScript (client)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
dist/
*.js.map
*.tsbuildinfo

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Benchmark / generated output
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
results/

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Secret / credential files  ← IMPORTANT
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
# Per-developer fresh-mode devnet deploy env files
# (program IDs only, no secret material — but the convention is to keep
# them out of the canonical history because each developer's IDs
# differ and shouldn't drive integrators' assumptions). Generated by
# scripts/ops/deploy-devnet.sh --fresh.
.env.devnet.*

# Solana wallet / keypair files (contain private keys)
id.json
*-keypair.json
*_keypair.json
wallet.json

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Python virtualenv (solana-tfmm-rs scripts)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# IDE / OS
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
Thumbs.db
.claude/worktrees/
reports/ab/pr-validation/history/
